#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:46
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:46
msgid "Customising This Display"
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:47
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:47
msgid ""
"The title field and the big Post Editing Area are fixed in place, but you "
"can reposition all the other boxes using drag and drop. You can also "
"minimise or expand them by clicking the title bar of each box. Use the "
"Screen Options tab to unhide more boxes (Location, Features, Property "
"Address, Pricing, Linked Contact, Featured Image, Excerpt, Discussion, "
"Comments, Slug, Author, Listing Details, Listing Features, Additional "
"Features, Files and Links) or to choose a 1- or 2-column layout for this "
"screen."
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:52
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:52
msgid ""
"Enter a title for your post, for best results enter the full property "
"address. After you enter a title, you’ll see the permalink below, which you "
"can edit."
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:54
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:54
msgid "Post editor"
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:54
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:54
msgid ""
"Enter the text for your post. There are two modes of editing: Visual and "
"Text. Choose the mode by clicking on the appropriate tab."
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:56
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:56
msgid ""
"Visual mode gives you a WYSIWYG editor. Click the last icon in the row to "
"get a second row of controls."
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:58
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:58
msgid ""
"The Text mode allows you to enter HTML along with your post text. Line "
"breaks will be converted to paragraphs automatically."
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:60
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:60
msgid ""
"You can insert media files by clicking the icons above the post editor and "
"following the directions. You can align or edit images using the inline "
"formatting toolbar available in Visual mode."
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:62
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:62
msgid ""
"You can enable distraction-free writing mode using the icon to the right. "
"This feature is not available for old browsers or devices with small "
"screens, and requires that the full-height editor be enabled in Screen "
"Options."
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:64
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:64
msgid ""
"Keyboard users: When you’re working in the visual editor, you can use "
"<code>Alt + F10</code> to access the toolbar."
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:69
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:69
msgid "Title and Post Editor"
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:75
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:75
msgid ""
"You can upload and insert media (images, audio, documents, etc.) by "
"clicking the Add Media button. You can select from the images and files "
"already uploaded to the Media Library, or upload new media to add to your "
"page or post. To manually create an image gallery, select the images to add "
"and click the “Create a new gallery” button."
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:77
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:77
msgid ""
"You can also embed media from many popular websites including Twitter, "
"YouTube, Flickr and others by pasting the media URL on its own line into "
"the content of your post/page. Please refer to the Codex to learn more "
"about embeds."
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:79
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:79
msgid "Note on Automatic Gallery Output:"
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:79
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:79
msgid ""
"When your Easy Property Listings gallery settings are set to automatic the "
"images that have been uploaded to this listing will automatically display "
"and you cannot control the image order or exclude images. For full gallery "
"control, disable the automatic gallery output and “Create a new gallery” "
"for each listing."
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:84
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:84
msgid "Inserting Media"
msgstr ""

