#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:103
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:103
msgid ""
"Add the full listing address and generate the coordinates for the listing. "
"You can drag the pin to adjust the lat/long coordinates of the listing. If "
"you do not check the \"Display Street Address\" option the street number "
"and street will not display to your visitor. You can also hide the map on a "
"per listing basis."
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:105
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:105
msgid ""
"If you do not check the \"Display Street Address\" option, the street "
"number and street will not display to your visitor."
msgstr ""

#: .claude/worktrees/strange-montalcini/lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:107
#: lib/includes/admin/help-single.php:107
msgid ""
"Adjust the lat/long coordinates of the listing by dragging the pin to a new "
"location if required. You can also hide the map on a per listing basis."
